<div class="dashboard-container">
  <header class="dashboard-header">
    <h1>VPN Setup Guide</h1>
  </header>

  <section class="setup-guide-section">
    <h2>How to Set Up Your VPN</h2>
    <p>Follow these steps to connect to your VPN using WireGuard:</p>

    <!-- Full instructions (copy from your current dashboard) -->
    <div class="setup-steps">
      <div class="step">
        <h3>1. Download WireGuard</h3>
        <p>Install the WireGuard app for your device:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/wireguard/id1441195209" target="_blank">iOS (App Store)</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wireguard.android" target="_blank">Android (Google Play)</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.wireguard.com/install/" target="_blank">Windows/macOS/Linux (Official Site)</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>2. Get Your Configuration</h3>
        <p>After subscribing, you received a QR code (for mobile) and a config file (for all devices).</p>
        <% if @has_subscription && @active_subscription %>
          <p><%= link_to "Download your config file", user_subscription_path(current_user, @active_subscription), class: "btn" %></p>
        <% else %>
          <p class="alert alert-warning" style="padding: 0.5rem; margin: 0.5rem 0;">ðŸ”’ Subscribe to download your config file.</p>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>3. Set Up the VPN</h3>
        <p><strong>Option A: QR Code (Mobile)</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>Open the WireGuard app.</li>
          <li>Tap <strong>"Add Tunnel" â†’ "Scan QR Code"</strong>.</li>
          <li>Scan the QR code from your dashboard.</li>
        </ol>
        <p><strong>Option B: Config File (All Devices)</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>Open the WireGuard app.</li>
          <li>Tap <strong>"Add Tunnel" â†’ "Import from file"</strong>.</li>
          <li>Select the downloaded config file.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>4. Connect to the VPN</h3>
        <p>Toggle the switch next to your tunnel to <strong>activate</strong> the connection.</p>
        <p>Verify your connection at <a href="https://whatismyip.com" target="_blank">whatismyip.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h3>5. Device Management</h3>
        <p>Your subscription includes configurations for up to 3 devices:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Each config file/QR code is for <strong>one device only</strong>.</li>
          <li>If you want to use the VPN on a new device, remove the configuration from one of your existing devices first.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Troubleshooting section (copy from your current dashboard) -->
  <section class="troubleshooting-section">
    <h2>Troubleshooting</h2>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question">
        Connection Issues <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p><strong>Symptoms:</strong> The VPN fails to connect or has connection problems.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Check for duplicate configurations:</strong> Ensure each config file/QR code is used on only one device. If the same configuration is installed on multiple devices, remove it from all but one device.</li>
          <li>Check your internet connection.</li>
          <li>Restart the VPN client.</li>
          <li>Restart your device.</li>
          <li>Check for firewall/antivirus interference.</li>
          <li>Reinstall the VPN configuration.</li>
          <li>Update the VPN app.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question">
        Connection Drops <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p><strong>Symptoms:</strong> The VPN disconnects frequently or fails to connect.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Check your internet connection.</li>
          <li>Restart the VPN client.</li>
          <li>Restart your device.</li>
          <li>Check for firewall/antivirus interference.</li>
          <li>Reinstall the VPN configuration.</li>
          <li>Update the VPN app.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question">
        Slow Speeds <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p><strong>Symptoms:</strong> The VPN connection is active, but browsing/downloads are slower than usual.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Test your base internet speed.</li>
          <li>Close background applications.</li>
          <li>Check for network congestion.</li>
          <li>Restart your router.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question">
        Unable to Access Certain Websites <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p><strong>Symptoms:</strong> Some websites or services are blocked or unavailable while connected to the VPN.</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Clear your browser cache.</li>
          <li>Disable IPv6.</li>
          <li>Check for DNS leaks.</li>
          <li>Contact support.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <button class="faq-question">
        General Tips <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
      </button>
      <div class="faq-answer">
        <p>Keep your app updated and check for announcements. If issues persist, contact support at <a href="mailto:support@FenguardVPN.com">support@fenguardvpn.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<style>
  /* Container and header */
  .dashboard-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background-color: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .dashboard-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .dashboard-header h1 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  /* Section styles */
  .setup-guide-section,
  .troubleshooting-section {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .setup-guide-section h2,
  .troubleshooting-section h2 {
    color: #2c3e50;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }

  /* Setup steps */
  .setup-steps {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .step {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .step:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .step h3 {
    color: #27ae60;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .step p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .step ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
  }

  .step li {
    padding: 0.3rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .step li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .step a {
    color: #3498db;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .step a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .step ol {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0 1.5rem;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .step ol li {
    margin: 0.3rem 0;
    list-style-type: decimal;
  }

  /* Alerts */
  .alert {
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }

  .alert-warning {
    background-color: #fff3cd;
    color: #856404;
    border-left: 4px solid #ffeeba;
  }

  /* Buttons */
  .btn {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 300px;
    background-color: #28a745;
    color: white !important;
    padding: 10px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 1em;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin: 15px auto;
